1428
00:43:50,670 --> 00:43:51,920
Dot, dot.

1429
00:43:53,950 --> 00:43:55,430
Dot, dash.

1430
00:44:11,280 --> 00:44:12,530
Hi, Sam.

1431
00:44:18,950 --> 00:44:21,410
