1433
00:44:26,000 --> 00:44:27,580
Dot, dot.

1434
00:44:29,060 --> 00:44:30,520
Dot, dash...

1435
00:44:40,020 --> 00:44:42,000
I need to get out of this house.

1436
00:44:42,400 --> 00:44:43,820
